articles.author: Jacob Lev
articles.title: New York Knicks extend Eastern Conference Finals against Indiana Pacers with statement Game 5 win - CNN
articles.description: “Knicks in 7” chants echoed around “The World’s Most Famous Arena” on Thursday night as the duo of Jalen Brunson and Karl-Anthony Towns led the New York Knicks to an Eastern Conference Finals-extending 111-94 win over the Indiana Pacers.
